JIM MEEHAN: Yes!

00:42:13.050 --> 00:42:15.591
AUDIENCE: And I was just curious
what your favorite bar there

00:42:15.591 --> 00:42:17.340
is.

00:42:17.340 --> 00:42:19.427
JIM MEEHAN: Oh, my gosh.

